cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.LG

The paper discusses privacy protection measures for sensitive textual data, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Databases (cs.DB), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). However, the focus on document redaction and sanitization, as well as the use of semantic models, makes cs.CR and cs.IR the most likely categories.
